history.content: So, one big issue is that 168 is normally not webcasted due to professor pedagogy. That means they are limited by lecture hall size (not just money for TAs). If the professor who is gonna teach it now follows suit, it probably wont be expanded, so I wouldn't bet on it expanding. That being said, 10% rule says at least 50 will drop, so you have a good chance of getting in. Good luck
